OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry this evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Turning cloudy from
OL,8,Fthe east overnight with a few mist
OL,9,Fpatches possible. Staying warm
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAny low cloud quickly lifting
OL,13,Fand clearing giving another very warm
OL,14,Fand sunny day with a brisk breeze
OL,15,Facross the region.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,18,FRemaining very warm, dry and sunny in
OL,19,Fthe outlook, although an easterly
OL,20,Fbreeze will bring a little relief to
OL,21,Fthe hot conditions.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
